<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NeonX Support</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Segoe+UI:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #f9fafb;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* Sidebar */

        .content h1,
        .content h2 {
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .content p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .tips {
            background: #eef;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="main">
        <style>
            .feedback-form {
                background-color: #2563eb;
                border: none;
                color: white;
                padding: 10px;
                margin: 20px;
            }
        </style>
        <button class="feedback-form" onclick="goBack()">
            Go Back
        </button>
        <script>
            function goBack() {
                if (window.history.length > 1) {
                    window.history.back();
                } else {
                    window.location.href = "index.html"; // fallback page
                }
            }
        </script>
        <!-- Seller Info -->
        <div class="seller-box">
            <h2>

                Send neonx feedbacks or noticable problems
                <div class="hideos feedback-form">
                    <form class="tips" action="/supports/<%=user._id%>/<%=user.username %>/<%=user.email%>"
                        method="POST">
                        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Write your feedback..." required></textarea>
                        <br> <button type="submit" onclick="alert('thanks for your feedback')">Submit Feedback</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </h2>

        </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h1 id="about">About NeonX</h1>
            <p>NeonX is a modern marketplace where you can buy, sell, and promote products securely. Whether it‚Äôs
                houses,
                cars, gadgets, or fashion items, NeonX connects buyers and sellers with ease.</p>
            <div class="tips"><strong>Tip:</strong> Keep your profile updated so users trust your listings more.</div>

            <h2 id="sell">How to Sell</h2>
            <p>1. Create an account and log in.<br>2. Go to the <em>Post Ad</em> section.<br>3. Select the correct
                category.<br>4. Upload clear pictures of your item.<br>5. Write a detailed description and set a fair
                price.<br>6. Publish your ad.</p>
            <div class="tips"><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Ads with high-quality photos and honest descriptions get more
                buyers.</div>

            <h2 id="buy">How to Buy</h2>
            <p>1. Use the search bar or category filters to find products.<br>2. Contact the seller via the in-app
                messaging
                system.<br>3. Arrange for safe viewing and negotiation.<br>4. Never pay before seeing the product.</p>
            <div class="tips"><strong>Safety:</strong> Always meet sellers in public places during the day.</div>

            <h2 id="vip">VIP & Boosting</h2>
            <p><strong>VIP:</strong> Upgrade your account to VIP and enjoy more visibility, trust, and faster
                sales.<br><br>
                <strong>Boosting:</strong> Boost your ads to appear at the top of search results for more exposure.
            </p>
            <div class="tips"><strong>Note:</strong> VIP and Boosting are optional, but they significantly increase your
                chances of selling fast.</div>

