            <p>We take your security seriously. Your password is encrypted, and your personal data is protected.<br><br>
                - Always log out after use.<br>
                - Don‚Äôt share your password.<br>
                - Report suspicious ads immediately.</p>
            <div class="tips"><strong>Reminder:</strong> NeonX will never ask for your password via email.</div>

            <h2 id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p><strong>Q: Is NeonX free?</strong><br>A: Yes, posting ads is free. VIP & Boosting are paid features for
                extra
                benefits.</p>

